        "type": "UncertaintyQuantification",
        "method": "Monte Carlo propagation of inlet flow-rate measurement uncertainty (±0.05 L/min) and rotational speed uncertainty (±10 RPM); 95% confidence interval on predicted pressure head ±3.8%.",
