      "description": "Planar PIV measurements in the volute region at 4 L/min, 3000 RPM compared to RANS predictions. Velocity magnitude agreement within 8% in the blade passage; recirculation zone extent matched to within one blade pitch. Grid-convergence index (GCI) computed on three mesh levels (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.7M cells); GCI < 2.3% on all reported QoIs.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/morrison-vr-velocity-uq",
        "type": "UncertaintyQuantification",
        "method": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI on three systematically refined meshes; experimental uncertainty from PIV calibration (±1.5% full-scale) propagated analytically.",
        "coverageProbability": 0.95
      }
    },
