      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs directly linked to COU decision criterion (RH < 1); hemolysis index and shear stress distribution confirmed as appropriate surrogates.",
      "rationale": "NIH and RH index are standard FDA-recognized hemolysis QoIs for blood-contacting devices. Power-law damage accumulation model (Giersiepen et al.) selected based on published validation studies. QoI traceability to COU decision documented in credibility plan CP-2023-01."
