      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected after three-model comparison (k-epsilon RNG, SST k-omega, RSM); SST k-omega gave lowest validation error on pressure head and velocity field. Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model selected based on published benchmark performance. Model form uncertainty acknowledged and bounded via parametric study."
