      "rationale": "Fluid properties sourced from calibrated rheometry (viscosity ±2%, density ±0.5%). Pump geometry from CMM-measured CAD (tolerance ±0.05 mm). Inlet velocity profile from PIV measurements. Input uncertainty propagated via LHS (n=500) to NIH index; 90th-percentile bound reported. Meets Gradation 2."
