      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single pump specimen used for validation consistent with MRL 2 scoping.",
      "rationale": "Single FDA generic pump specimen used for all validation experiments. Sample-to-sample variability not characterized at MRL 2. Scoped out per credibility plan CP-2023-01. Acceptable for Class II device at MRL 2."
